content: Love this app! My son loves it too! We have it on every nap time :) the washing machine is his favourite lol. Well worth purchasing the pro version!

replyContent: Hello Yuhsuan, the purchase is tied with the account on the Play Store. You need to switch to the same account used for the purchase and install the Unlock again. For more details, please contact support@urbandroid.org. Thank you.
